Nestle Sees Organic Growth at Top End of Range After Sales Beat Estimates

-- B y   C e l e s t e   P e r r i
-- 
2011-08-10T05:20:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-10/nestle-sees-full-year-organic-sales-growth-at-top-end-of-forecasted-range.html
Nestle SA (NESN) , the world’s largest
foodmaker, said it sees full-year organic sales growth at the
top end of its 5 percent to 6 percent range after reporting
first-half sales that topped analysts’ estimates.  Nestle also expects a margin increase in constant
currencies for the year, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at 
 cperri@bloomberg.net  